<p><a name="References" id="References"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Geometric_algebra&amp;action=edit&amp;section=44" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFArtin1957">Artin, Emil (1957). <i>Geometric Algebra</i>. Interscience Publishers.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Geometric+Algebra&amp;rft.aulast=Artin&amp;rft.aufirst=Emil&amp;rft.au=Artin%2C+Emil&amp;rft.date=1957&amp;rft.pub=Interscience+Publishers&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Geometric_algebra"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFClifford.2C_W.1878">Clifford, W. (1878). "Applications of Grassmann's Extensive Algebra". <i>American Journal of Mathematics</i> <b>1</b> (4): 350â€“358. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F2369379" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.2307%2F2369379" rel="nofollow">10.2307/2369379</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Applications+of+Grassmann%27s+Extensive+Algebra&amp;rft.jtitle=American+Journal+of+Mathematics&amp;rft.aulast=Clifford%2C+W.&amp;rft.au=Clifford%2C+W.&amp;rft.date=1878&amp;rft.volume=1&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=350%E2%80%93358&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.2307%2F2369379&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Geometric_algebra"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li>Leo Dorst, Daniel Fontijne, Stephen Mann, "<a href="http://www.geometricalgebra.net/" class="external text" title="http://www.geometricalgebra.net/" rel="nofollow">Geometric Algebra for Computer Science: An Object-Oriented Approach to Geometry</a>" (The Morgan Kaufmann Series in Computer Graphics), Morgan Kaufmann (April 19, 2007), ISBN-10: 0123694655, ISBN-13: 978-0123694652.</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFGrassmann1844">Grassmann, Hermann (1844). <i><a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=bKgAAAAAMAAJ&amp;pg=PA1&amp;dq=Die+Lineale+Ausdehnungslehre+ein+neuer+Zweig+der+Mathematik" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=bKgAAAAAMAAJ&amp;pg=PA1&amp;dq=Die+Lineale+Ausdehnungslehre+ein+neuer+Zweig+der+Mathematik" rel="nofollow">Die Lineale Ausdehnungslehre - Ein neuer Zweig der Mathematik</a></i>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=%5Bhttp%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DbKgAAAAAMAAJ%26pg%3DPA1%26dq%3DDie%2BLineale%2BAusdehnungslehre%2Bein%2Bneuer%2BZweig%2Bder%2BMathematik+Die+Lineale+Ausdehnungslehre+-+Ein+neuer+Zweig+der+Mathematik%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Grassmann&amp;rft.aufirst=Hermann&amp;rft.au=Grassmann%2C+Hermann&amp;rft.date=1844&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Geometric_algebra"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> (The Linear Extension Theory - A new Branch of Mathematics)</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFHestenes1966">Hestenes, David (1966). <i>Space-time Algebra</i>. Gordon and Breach.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Space-time+Algebra&amp;rft.aulast=Hestenes&amp;rft.aufirst=David&amp;rft.au=Hestenes%2C+David&amp;rft.date=1966&amp;rft.pub=Gordon+and+Breach&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Geometric_algebra"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/David_Hestenes" title="David Hestenes">David Hestenes</a> and Sobczyk, G., 1984. <i>Clifford Algebra to Geometric Calculus</i>, Springer Verlag <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9027716730" class="internal">ISBN 90-277-1673-0</a></li>
</ul>
